<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sindika Storage API - Manajemen Dokumen Gereja</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        .feature-card {
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .gradient-bg {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-emerald-50 to-teal-50 min-h-screen">
        <header class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-xl border-b border-white/20">
        <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
            <nav class="flex justify-between items-center py-5">
                <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">
                    Sindika
                </a>
                <div class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-10">
                    <a href="#fitur" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors duration-300 font-medium">Fitur Unggulan</a>
                    <a href="#analitik" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors duration-300 font-medium">Analitik & AI</a>
                    <a href="/solusi" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors duration-300 font-medium">Solusi Kami</a>
                    <a href="/core-platform" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors duration-300 font-medium">Core Platform</a>
                    <a href="/sindi-ai" class="font-bold text-blue-600 transition-colors duration-300">SINDI AI</a>
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="hidden md:inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-2.5 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
                    Jadwalkan Demo
                </a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 pt-32 pb-16">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 rounded-2xl mb-6">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 19a2 2 0 01-2-2V7a2 2 0 012-2h4l2 2h4a2 2 0 012 2v1M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2v-5a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Storage API</h1>
            <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium text-emerald-600 mb-6">Pusat Dokumen Gereja yang Aman</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Kelola semua dokumen penting gereja Anda dengan aman. Dari notulensi majelis, laporan keuangan, hingga materi pembinaan jemaat—semuanya tersimpan terpusat dan terorganisir dengan baik.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-12">
            <div class="feature-card p-8 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 7v10a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-6l-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Organisasi Dokumen Rapi</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600">Pisahkan dokumen berdasarkan kategori: notulensi majelis, laporan keuangan, materi katekisasi, surat keputusan, dan arsip sejarah gereja—semua terstruktur dengan rapi.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card p-8 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Akses Berbasis Peran</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600">Kontrol siapa yang bisa melihat apa. Majelis akses penuh, komisi lihat dokumen pelayanan mereka, jemaat akses materi umum—semuanya teratur dan aman.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card p-8 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Riwayat & Versi Dokumen</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600">Lacak setiap perubahan dokumen penting. Siapa yang upload, kapan direvisi, dan akses versi sebelumnya—transparansi penuh untuk akuntabilitas gereja.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card p-8 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-orange-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Backup Otomatis</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600">Dokumen penting gereja tidak akan pernah hilang. Sistem backup otomatis menjaga sejarah dan arsip gereja tetap aman untuk generasi mendatang.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 p-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl text-white text-center">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Akhiri Era Dokumen Berantakan</h3>
            <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-emerald-100">Tidak perlu lagi mencari dokumen di lemari arsip atau email. Semua dokumen gereja ada di satu tempat yang aman dan mudah diakses.</p>
            <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-emerald-600 font-semibold rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition-all">
                Mulai Kelola Dokumen Gereja
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
                </svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>